    public abstract class AbstractPrimitive
extends java.lang.Object
implements Primitive
    The superclass of all primitives. This class defines the behaviour of all primitives and made the common operations to all of them.

      • updateVersion

        protected void updateVersion()
        Increases the version number and updates the cached code to a new version. These changes are done for all of the classes in the inheritance tree of the modified class, so, all of the tree evolves to a new version.
